The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 06 November is 975,504 (1,733.1 cases per 100,000 population). In the seven days to 01 November, there were 130,454 new confirmed cases (231.8 new cases per 100,000). In the seven days to 25 October, there were 129,230 new cases and so the new cases have risen by 1% ( 1,224 extra cases).
